---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="SocialProof vs EmbedSocial — Which is right for testimonials? | SocialProof" description="EmbedSocial starts at $29/mo and is built for social media aggregation. SocialProof is $9/mo and built specifically for collecting + displaying customer testimonials." canonical="https://socialproof.dev/vs/embedsocial">
<style>

    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; margin: 0; background: #fff; color: #111; }
    nav { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
    nav a.logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.25rem; color: #111; text-decoration: none; }
    nav .nav-links a { margin-left: 1.5rem; color: #555; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    nav .cta-nav { background: #111; color: #fff !important; padding: .45rem 1rem; border-radius: 6px; }
    .hero { text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .vs-badge { display: inline-block; background: #f0f0f0; color: #555; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .06em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: .35rem .75rem; border-radius: 99px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
    .hero h1 span { color: #4f46e5; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.15rem; color: #444; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }
    .hero-cta { display: inline-block; background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; padding: .85rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; }
    .hero-cta:hover { background: #3730a3; }
    .price-callout { display: inline-flex; gap: 2rem; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px solid #e5e5e5; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.25rem 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .price-callout .item { text-align: center; }
    .price-callout .item .price { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; }
    .price-callout .item .label { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #777; margin-top: .2rem; }
    .price-callout .item.vouch .price { color: #4f46e5; }
    .price-callout .item.other .price { color: #dc2626; }
    section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 2rem; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .compare-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .compare-table th { padding: .75rem 1rem; text-align: left; font-size: 0.85rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .05em; color: #888; border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; }
    .compare-table th:nth-child(2) { color: #4f46e5; }
    .compare-table td { padding: .85rem 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; font-size: 0.97rem; vertical-align: top; }
    .compare-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
    .compare-table td:first-child { color: #555; font-weight: 500; }
    .yes { color: #16a34a; font-weight: 600; }
    .no { color: #dc2626; font-weight: 600; }
    .partial { color: #d97706; font-weight: 600; }
    .winner-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .winner-card { border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.75rem; }
    .winner-card.vouch { background: #f0fdf4; border: 1px solid #86efac; }
    .winner-card.other { background: #fafafa; border: 1px solid #e5e5e5; }
    .winner-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 .75rem; }
    .winner-card ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.25rem; color: #444; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.8; }
    .savings-box { background: #eff6ff; border: 1px solid #93c5fd; border-radius: 12px; padding: 2rem; text-align: center; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .savings-box .amount { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: #1d4ed8; }
    .savings-box p { color: #1e40af; margin: .5rem 0 0; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .vs-links { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 1rem; }
    .vs-links a { color: #4f46e5; font-size: 0.95rem; text-decoration: none; }
    .vs-links a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    .cta-section { background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem; }
    .cta-section h2 { color: #fff; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .cta-section p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 1.05rem; }
    .cta-btn { display: inline-block; background: #fff; color: #4f46e5; padding: .85rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; }
    .cta-btn:hover { background: #f0f0ff; }
    footer { text-align: center; padding: 2rem; color: #999; font-size: 0.85rem; border-top: 1px solid #eee; }
    footer a { color: #777; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 .75rem; }
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .winner-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .price-callout { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
    }
  
</style>
<div class="hero">
  <span class="vs-badge">SocialProof vs EmbedSocial</span>
  <h1>EmbedSocial aggregates social feeds.<br /><span>SocialProof collects real testimonials.</span></h1>
  <p>EmbedSocial is a powerful tool for pulling in Instagram, Facebook, and Google content. If what you actually need is to collect and display customer testimonials, SocialProof does that job better — and at a fraction of the price.</p>

  <div class="price-callout">
    <div class="item vouch">
      <div class="price">$9</div>
      <div class="label">SocialProof Pro / mo</div>
    </div>
    <div class="item other">
      <div class="price">$29+</div>
      <div class="label">EmbedSocial Basics / mo</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/register" class="hero-cta">Try SocialProof free — no card needed</a>
</div>

<section>
  <h2>Different tools for different jobs</h2>
  <p style="color:#555; margin-bottom:1.5rem;">EmbedSocial is built around social media aggregation — it pulls your Instagram posts, Facebook reviews, Google reviews, and TikTok content and displays them on your website. It's a broad platform for UGC (user-generated content) from social platforms.</p>
  <p style="color:#555; margin-bottom:1.5rem;">SocialProof is focused on one job: helping you collect fresh, structured testimonials from real customers via a shareable link, and displaying them on your site with a lightweight embeddable widget. No social API dependencies. No platform lock-in.</p>

  <table class="compare-table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Feature</th>
        <th>SocialProof</th>
        <th>EmbedSocial</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>Primary purpose</td>
        <td><span class="yes">Collect + display customer testimonials</span></td>
        <td>Social media aggregation (Instagram, Facebook, Google, TikTok)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Starting price</td>
        <td><span class="yes">Free → $9/mo Pro</span></td>
        <td><span class="no">$29/mo (7-day trial only)</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Free plan</td>
        <td><span class="yes">Free forever — 1 widget, 25 testimonials</span></td>
        <td><span class="no">No free plan — 7-day trial</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Collect testimonials via shareable link</td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ Auto-created on signup</span></td>
        <td><span class="no">✗ Pulls from social platforms only</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Works without social media accounts</td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ Fully independent</span></td>
        <td><span class="no">✗ Requires social platform connections</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Testimonial approval / moderation</td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ Built-in approval flow</span></td>
        <td><span class="partial">Limited — sourced from platforms</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Google rich results (JSON-LD stars)</td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ Pro plan</span></td>
        <td><span class="partial">Via Google Reviews widget only</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Custom branding removal</td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓ Pro plan ($9/mo)</span></td>
        <td><span class="partial">Higher-tier plans</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Embed with one script tag</td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓</span></td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Shopify, Wix, Squarespace support</td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓</span></td>
        <td><span class="yes">✓</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Platform dependency</td>
        <td><span class="yes">None — you own your testimonials</span></td>
        <td><span class="no">Dependent on social platform APIs</span></td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>The platform dependency risk</h2>
  <p style="color:#555; line-height:1.7;">EmbedSocial's power — and its weakness — is that it relies on social platform APIs. If Instagram changes its API (it has, many times), your embedded feed breaks. If your Google business listing gets flagged, your reviews widget goes dark.</p>
  <p style="color:#555; line-height:1.7;">With SocialProof, you own the testimonials. They live in your account, not on a third-party platform. If you want to move, export them. There's no API integration that can break your site.</p>

  <div class="savings-box">
    <div class="amount">Save $240/yr</div>
    <p>SocialProof Pro at $9/mo vs EmbedSocial Basics at $29/mo — that's $240 saved per year for a focused testimonial tool that actually collects new content.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Who wins in each scenario</h2>
  <div class="winner-grid">
    <div class="winner-card vouch">
      <h3>✅ Choose SocialProof if you…</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Want to collect fresh testimonials from customers (not just pull from social)</li>
        <li>Don't want to depend on Instagram, Facebook, or Google APIs</li>
        <li>Need a free plan that lasts longer than 7 days</li>
        <li>Want Google rich results / star ratings in search</li>
        <li>Run a service business, coaching practice, consulting firm, or e-commerce store</li>
        <li>Care about price — $9/mo vs $29+/mo is real money</li>
        <li>Want a simple, single-purpose tool without a sprawling dashboard</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="winner-card other">
      <h3>Consider EmbedSocial if you…</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Primarily need to embed Instagram, Facebook, or TikTok social feeds on your site</li>
        <li>Already have a strong presence on social platforms and want to repurpose that content</li>
        <li>Need a full UGC aggregation platform with social publishing features</li>
        <li>Budget isn't the primary concern and you need multi-platform management</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>The no-social-media business</h2>
  <p style="color:#555; line-height:1.7;">Not every small business is on Instagram or has a Google Business profile with reviews rolling in. A freelance consultant, a local coach, a B2B service provider — they often collect testimonials via email or conversation, not social platforms.</p>
  <p style="color:#555; line-height:1.7;">EmbedSocial has nothing to offer these businesses. SocialProof gives them a shareable link to send to any client, via any channel, and a widget to display the results — no social presence required.</p>
</section>

