  <h2>Try SocialProof free — no credit card needed</h2>
  <p>Get your collection link in 60 seconds. One script tag to embed. Free forever for 1 widget.</p>
  <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/register" class="cta-btn">Start collecting testimonials →</a>
